We just pushed a new features to all you guys and gals: Burst Protection.


I’m not saying that it ever happened to you, but you probably know someone, who knows someone, who’s cousin knows someone … well you get it. You released a new version of your software to production and suddenly everything starts failing. All of your users are frustrated and your operations team run around like headless chickens. When stuff like this is happening, your website typically logs a lot of errors. Depending on which 
